[ext_resource type="Script" path="res://scripts/interactables/mailbox.gd" id="1_mailbox"]

; Heritage Canada Post style — chunky red box on a short post, with a small
; cream slot near the top and a yellow flag on a thin pivot.
; The maple-leaf decal is faked with a small red prism on a cream patch — no
; texture needed and reads correctly at side-camera distance.

